"{\"uid\": \"perthnow.com.au-lifestyle-athletes-in-paris-olympic-village-to-be-provided-with-300000-condoms-as-intimacy-ban-lifted-at-games-c-14042205\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Get the FREE App  Get the FREE App  Organisers of the upcoming Paris Olympics are acutely aware that ripped bodies, high emotions and shared athlete headquarters are a recipe for sexual energy.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 193, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 63, \"end\": 77, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lifting the COVID-induced intimacy ban that plagued the Tokyo Games in 2021, powerbrokers have announced a generous supply of 300,000 condoms to ensure their 9000 hosted athletes take safe sex precautions.\", \"from\": 195, \"to\": 400, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Games chiefs toldSky Newsthey planned to reunite competitors in the city of love, providing enough prophylactics for each athlete to get back on the horse twice a day.\", \"from\": 402, \"to\": 569, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It is very important that the conviviality here is something big,\\\" Laurent Michaud, director of the village told the publication.\", \"from\": 571, \"to\": 701, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Working with the athletes commission, we wanted to create some places where the athletes would feel very enthusiastic and comfortable.\\\"\", \"from\": 703, \"to\": 839, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Beds in athlete's living quarters are reportedly built to hold up to 250kg - a single weight-lifter, or a couple of sprinters.\", \"from\": 841, \"to\": 967, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A Village Club has been created to encourage mixing across nations once again - an aphrodisiac sure to rev up competitors along with a few other French staples.\", \"from\": 969, \"to\": 1129, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1114, \"end\": 1120, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.6679277416443503, \"rank\": 0.4681353905892615, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We will have more than 350 metres of buffet with the world food... and I am sure that the athletes will be very happy to have some French specialties made over here,\\\" Mr Michaud said.\", \"from\": 1131, \"to\": 1315, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1263, \"end\": 1269, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.6679277416443503, \"rank\": 0.4681353905892615, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But the variety will first respond to the athletes' needs for their nutrition and their performance.\\\"\", \"from\": 1317, \"to\": 1419, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Fuelling their will to win, the variety in both food options and nationalities will likely also spur on their sex drive.\", \"from\": 1421, \"to\": 1541, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympic Village is said to be the single most expensive project at the Paris Games at $3.3 billion - largely funded by property investors.\", \"from\": 1543, \"to\": 1685, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1547, \"end\": 1562, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0507581087105275e-15, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"News  Split by the River Seine in the previously rundown area of Saint-Denis, the village is described as roughly the size of 70 soccer pitches.\", \"from\": 1687, \"to\": 1831, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1706, \"end\": 1717, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"River Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Paris 2024 Olympic and Paralympic Games will take place from July 26 to August 11.\", \"from\": 1833, \"to\": 1919, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1837, \"end\": 1847, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999993179, \"rank\": 7.491356996752945e-13, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1860, \"end\": 1876, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paralympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9990300875474795, \"rank\": 0.0009553621697459236, \"text\": \"Paralympic Games\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paralympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paralympic_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"News  News  News  News\", \"from\": 1921, \"to\": 1943, \"entities\": []}]}"